schema.prisma → Defines DB structure.

npx prisma migrate dev → Actually builds/updates DB tables.

lib/prisma.ts → Provides the Prisma client instance to query the DB.

app/api/users/route.ts → Uses Prisma to read/write from DB, exposes it as HTTP API endpoints (/api/users).

app/page.tsx → React component that calls the API, manages state, and displays data to the user.